1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) - The paper deals with feature representation and classification of hyperspectral remote sensing data, which is a common problem in computer vision and pattern recognition. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed method involves feature learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. 
3. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper deals with feature selection and extraction, which are important tasks in information retrieval. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a novel feature learning framework, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with hyperspectral remote sensing data, which can be considered as a type of multimedia data.
